<plot>A psychologist by the name of Dr. Ruth Miller relives her abusive childhood through an encounter with a patient named Katie. Through her encounter with Katie, memories of her abusive past resurface. It turns out that Miller was raped horribly as a child by a priest, Fr. Monte, that her Aunt Sally trusted to look after Miller. Miller ends up repressing these memories as an adult, only to discover these memories again. Miller is then faced to fight her demons once and for all or remain a prisoner of her past.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?190910</url></doc>
